profile: Our locally owned and operated store has been proudly serving the community of Comox Valley and surrounding areas for over 24 years. We understand the needs of customers in the Comox Valley, because we’re from here. Come visit our Courtenay location and let us show you the Nufloors beautiful experience.  We supply and Install – Hardwood Floors – Laminate Flooring – Tile  Flooring – Sheet Vinyl Flooring  – Luxury Vinyl – Carpet Flooring.
